        "description": {
          "type": "description",
          "settings": {
            "read_more": true,
            "style": "accordions",
            "title_1": "Benefits",
            "raw_content_1": "<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">4-minute leave-in treatment to reverse hair damage</p><ul><li><strong>K18PEPTIDE™ </strong>is a biotech-developed peptide that mimics hair's structure to reverse damage by reconnecting polypeptide chains and disulfide bonds broken during bleaching, color and chemical services + heat.</li><li><strong>pH-optimized (5.0-6.0): </strong>Helps minimize cuticle swelling + put hair proteins in their most resilient state</li><li><strong>Cream format:</strong> Enables easy, lightweight application across all hair types, with detangling and softening benefits</li></ul><p>Vegan, color-safe, cruelty-free</p>",
            "title_2": "How To Use",
            "raw_content_2": "<ol><li><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">Shampoo with </span><a href=\"https://www.hairmnl.com/products/k18-damage-shield-ph-protective-shampoo-250ml\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">K18 Damage Shield PH Protective Shampoo</span></a><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"> or </span><a href=\"https://www.hairmnl.com/products/k18-peptide-prep-detox-shampoo-250ml\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">K18 Peptide Prep™ Detox Shampoo</span></a><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">, do not condition. Towel-dry thoroughly</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">Apply 3-9 pumps of </span><strong>K18 Leave-In Molecular Repair Mask</strong><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"> based on your length and density, starting at the ends and working up towards the roots</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">Let sit for 4 minutes. Do not rinse out.</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">Comb, add product + style as usual. Use for consecutively for 4-6 washes post-salon service, then as needed</span></li></ol>",
            "title_3": "Ingredients",
            "raw_content_3": "Water (Aqua) (Eau), Alcohol Denat., Propylene Glycol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Dicaprylyl Ether, Cetyl Esters, Behentrimonium Chloride, Polysorbate 20,sh-Oligopeptide-78 (K18PEPTIDE™), Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Hydrolyzed Wheat Starch, Isopropyl Alcohol, Tocopherol, Phenoxyethanol, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid, Fragrance (Parfum), Geraniol, Linalool, Hexyl Cinnamal, Benzyl Alcohol.",
            "title_4": "",
            "raw_content_4": "",
